---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<section
	class="flex flex-col text-center gap-11 md:gap-0 md:text-start md:flex-row max-w-[1290px] justify-around py-10 border rounded-[20px] border-card-primary shadow-card-primary dark:shadow-none dark:border-card-primary-dark/[8%] dark:bg-card-primary-dark/[16%] backdrop-blur-sm"
>
	<div class="max-w-[346px] mx-auto">
		<div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
			<Icon
				icon="terminal-window"
				color="fill-icon-primary dark:fill-icon-primary-dark stroke-icon-primary dark:stroke-icon-primary-dark"
				size="2.5rem"
			/>
			<h2
				class="text-2xl font-bold text-skin-base dark:text-skin-base-dark ml-4"
			>
				Full Stack
			</h2>
		</div>
		<p class="mt-4 font-medium text-skin-muted dark:text-skin-muted-dark">
			Strong background in full stack development and cloud infrastructure.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="max-w-[346px] mx-auto">
		<div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
			<Icon
				icon="trophy"
				size="2.5rem"
				color="fill-icon-primary dark:fill-icon-primary-dark stroke-icon-primary dark:stroke-icon-primary-dark"
			/>
			<h2
				class="text-2xl font-bold text-skin-base dark:text-skin-base-dark ml-4"
			>
				Knowledge Driven
			</h2>
		</div>
		<p class="mt-4 font-medium text-skin-muted dark:text-skin-muted-dark">
			Continuously keeping up to date with new technologies and in line with
			leading industry standards.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="max-w-[346px] mx-auto">
		<div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
			<Icon
				icon="strategy"
				size="2.5rem"
				color="fill-icon-primary dark:fill-icon-primary-dark stroke-icon-primary dark:stroke-icon-primary-dark"
			/>
			<h2
				class="text-2xl font-bold text-skin-base dark:text-skin-base-dark ml-4"
			>
				Strategy-Minded
			</h2>
		</div>
		<p class="mt-4 font-medium text-skin-muted dark:text-skin-muted-dark">
			Developing and executing effective plans and strategies to achive
			long-term goals.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>
